## 15. Prioritized Remediation Roadmap

### Phase 1: Immediate (Week 1-2)

| Priority | Vulnerability | Action |
|----------|---------------|--------|
| 🔴 | V1.1 - Hardcoded JWT Secret | Move to vault, implement rotation |
| 🔴 | V4.1 - CSRF Verification | Confirm and test CSRF middleware |
| 🟠 | V5.1 - File Upload Validation | Implement content-based validation |
| 🟠 | V8.1 - Debug Mode in Example | Update `.env.example` |

### Phase 2: Short-term (Week 3-6)

| Priority | Vulnerability | Action |
|----------|---------------|--------|
| 🟠 | V1.2 - Weak Default Password | Generate random passwords |
| 🟠 | V1.3 - JWT Expiration | Add explicit validation |
| 🟠 | V2.1 - DB::raw() Usage | Refactor to selectRaw() |
| 🟡 | V6.1 - Session Lifetime | Reduce to 30 minutes |

### Phase 3: Medium-term (Month 2-3)

| Priority | Vulnerability | Action |
|----------|---------------|--------|
| 🟡 | V2.2 - Input Sanitization | Add length limits, sanitization |
| 🟡 | V3.1 - XSS Protection | Frontend audit, implement CSP |
| 🟡 | V7.1 - Database Encryption | Enable SSL/TLS for MySQL |
| 🟡 | V9.1 - Sensitive Logging | Remove session IDs from logs |

